column2: test <- map(seq(5,30,1),
function(y){
res.efa <- fa(r = df_ambi_cor, scores = "tenBerge",
nfactors = y, rotate= "bentlerT", fm="uls")
function(x){
r <- f_EFA_testsimple(res.efa$loadings, x)
res <- (r$n_factor_perc + r$n_load_perc)/2
return(res)
}) %>% as_vector
return(res.f)
